
admin can add study material to the system. The study material includes a name, a note URL, and a video URL. 
add Study material option on navbar if the user is admin.there admin can see all the study materials on the system. there should be option to create new study  material. 
on creating study material, on frontend show upload button for notes and videos. on uploading take its location path and pass it to string as on backend. also on each study material there should be option to edit and delete the study material. admin can take the detailed view of the study material and when taking detailed view, there should be option to assign study material to students or delete study material from students. admin can assign study material to students by selecting the students from the list of students in the system.
on study material detailed view. add extra two button along with update and delete called, assign and unassign. on normal listing there should be only update and delete button. 
POST /api/studymaterials/{{materialId}}/assign/{{internId}}

